294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334760/extras/2e87e64367343975c4a0fef55e268dde.mp4?t=1763677294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore the different set pieces from forests and caves to fields and dungeons. Interact with the world to solve puzzles and find hidden passages in order to continue your journey. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334760/extras/f6c181895c02a95c41695014ab0261f5.poster.avif?t=1763677294\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334760/extras/f6c181895c02a95c41695014ab0261f5.webm?t=1763677294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334760/extras/f6c181895c02a95c41695014ab0261f5.mp4?t=1763677294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334760/extras/c61c5be049edd3d4245e65667905611e.poster.avif?t=1763677294\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334760/extras/c61c5be049edd3d4245e65667905611e.webm?t=1763677294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334760/extras/c61c5be049edd3d4245e65667905611e.mp4?t=1763677294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In this adventure you play a young man named Milo, who comes upon a nearby forest after his home is devastated by the Tares of Bedlam. Searching for personal aid, he discovers his destiny is intertwined with the fate of the realm. Set out and explore a wide world full of adventure while learning of the mystery of the Elderseed to forestall the coming chaos.",
